29:35.307 --> 29:36.640
Happy birthday, Mi!

29:38.077 --> 29:41.445
- Honey, I'm so sorry we
didn't get you a dress today.

29:41.447 --> 29:43.080
- It's fine.

29:46.952 --> 29:50.954
- So, how did Amy know
about my drinking?

29:50.956 --> 29:53.290
- Mom, you have an AA
card on the fridge.

29:54.960 --> 29:56.860
- Did she talk to you about it?

29:56.862 --> 29:58.428
- No. Of course not.

29:58.430 --> 30:02.833
