30:50.683 --> 30:53.584
- Where? Some crappy
consignment store?

30:53.586 --> 30:56.587
Oh, or the outlet mall? Ugh!

30:56.589 --> 30:58.355
God! I mean, look at this!

30:58.357 --> 31:00.891
Cheap! Cheap! Ugly! Cheap!

31:00.893 --> 31:04.161
