32:06.659 --> 32:10.160
- I'm wondering if anyone
has ever filed a complaint

32:10.162 --> 32:11.795
against Amy Turner.

32:11.797 --> 32:13.297
- Not that I'm aware.

32:13.299 --> 32:16.433
- Not just teachers,
but students.

32:16.435 --> 32:17.601
- Of course not.

32:17.603 --> 32:20.037
And I'm sure if there
were any issues,

32:20.039 --> 32:21.438
they were dealt with,

32:21.440 --> 32:23.507
since we strongly
encourage our teachers

32:23.509 --> 32:25.008
to handle things internally.

32:25.010 --> 32:27.611
I'm sure you can understand why.

32:27.613 --> 32:30.614
- Of course. Thank you.

32:35.287 --> 32:36.987
