steering clear?

32:44.964 --> 32:46.229
- I'm actually surprised

32:46.231 --> 32:48.165
no one's filed a
complaint against her.

32:48.167 --> 32:50.167
- Well, no one likes to admit

32:50.169 --> 32:52.002
