33:08.420 --> 33:10.487
- Well, make it easy.

33:10.489 --> 33:12.022
- I'll make it fair.

33:12.024 --> 33:15.192
Hey, do you know where I might
be able to find Ms. Saunders?

33:15.194 --> 33:16.693
- In the teacher directory.

33:16.695 --> 33:19.663
