33:38.250 --> 33:41.284
Hi! Uh, are you Carol Saunders?

33:41.286 --> 33:42.953
- Yes. Can I help you?

33:42.955 --> 33:44.454
- I'm Julie Taylor.

33:44.456 --> 33:46.857
